00:35:54,026 --> 00:35:55,527
Yes.

517
00:35:59,907 --> 00:36:03,785
I hate that this is happening to me.
I hate it too.

518
00:36:04,745 --> 00:36:07,664
We have to keep the important
things in our life going.

519
00:36:07,874 --> 00:36:10,083
We have to try
or we're going to go crazy.

520
00:36:10,293 --> 00:36:11,668
I know. I know, John.

