970
01:09:57,401 --> 01:09:59,110
I am struggling.

971
01:09:59,320 --> 01:10:02,906
Struggling to be a part of things,

972
01:10:03,115 --> 01:10:08,119
to stay connected to who I once was.

973
01:10:09,622 --> 01:10:12,457
